  // 2. execute(variables):
  //    - capture the CURRENT data value as `snapshot` (the specific pre-update state to roll back to)
  //    - immediately setData(applyOptimistic(current, variables)) using the functional updater
  //      to always read the latest state, not a stale closure
  //    - set isPending true, clear error
  //    - await mutate(variables)
  //    - on success: setData(serverResult)
  //    - on failure: setData(snapshot) to roll back to what it was before THIS call, set error
  //    - use an isMountedRef guard so setState calls after unmount are no-ops

