  // 2. Row onDragStart: setDraggedId(getId(item)); optionally set drag image
  // 3. Row onDragOver (preventDefault required to allow drop!): compute whether
  //    cursor is in the top or bottom half of the row to decide insert-before
  //    vs insert-after, setDropTargetIndex accordingly
  // 4. Row/container onDrop: compute the reordered array by removing the dragged
  //    item and reinserting it at dropTargetIndex, call onReorder, reset state
  // 5. onDragEnd (fires on cancel too, e.g. Escape or drop outside): reset all
  //    drag-related state regardless of whether a drop happened
  // 6. Render a visual indicator line at dropTargetIndex while dragging

